name: Artisanal Lighting of the 4th Dimension V2-Glitch
description:
@ArtPunkDude | Lights, Procedural Coils, Colour unachievable by archaic electric resistance bulbs in the flimsy universal context of time and space and physics tied to it.

Possible However In a Digital Simulated Multiverse. 

On A Personal Note, the Artist of this Used to Design Lighting for Theatre Shows. Then Covid Hit. Now Said Artist Likes Making Impossible Lights In Digital Forms as an Ode to a time probably lost. Also, Looking into some glitch and experimenting.

This Is V2-Glitch. One Collector Of "Artisanal Lighting of the 4th Dimension V2" Will Get this 1/1 Edition For Free, which will be the only way to get it from the Artist.
